The paper deals with the modal logic of knowledge in multi-agent systems, which falls under the category of logic (cs.LO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses distributed and multi-agent systems, which are relevant to distributed computing (cs.DC) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). Finally, the paper provides an axiomatization of the logic, which is related to formal languages and automata theory (cs.LG).
